  "synopsis": "After a night of playing \"Savior Rising,\" Daud Campbell wakes up in the game as an unimpressive minor character. Despite his plans to lay low and avoid trouble, he runs into both the final boss and the main hero on his first day at the game's academy. As Daud struggles to make it through the game, he only seems to attract more danger, including the attention of evil characters. Will the love of these powerful villains help Daud survive till the end? Or are they just too wicked for his own good?\n\n(Source: Tapas)\n\n*Note: Includes one extra chapter.*",
